{"date":"2018-10-06","platform":"TV","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/7d/9a/236510_wa77s.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/7d/9a/236510_wa77s.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/7d/9a/236510_wa77s.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/7d/9a/236510_wa77s.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/7d/9a/236510_wa77s.jpg"},"summary":"源桃是住在空崎市的女高中生。原本过着平凡生活的她，由于某件事而被私设情报机关“月影”选中。\r\n月影是不属于任何国家、在暗中守护和平的正义间谍组织。以只对年轻女性有效、能够提升能力的特制香料为首的种种秘密道具，以及历经磨练的身心，就是她们战斗的武器。\r\n还是新人的桃，受到组织里的前辈、同时也是高中前辈的半藏门雪的照顾。\r\n月影存在着师徒制度，由前辈锻炼后辈，并让后辈继承自己的技术。\r\n现在，犯罪组织“魍魉”将魔手伸向了大都市空崎。桃为了保护自己身边的家人、朋友以及商店街的人们，而与同伴齐心协力铲除邪恶。","name":"RELEASE THE SPYCE","name_cn":"月影特工","tags":[{"name":"原创","count":546,"total_cont":0},{"name":"百合","count":537,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2018年10月","count":450,"total_cont":0},{"name":"TV","count":315,"total_cont":0},{"name":"战斗","count":306,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Lay-duce","count":239,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2018","count":195,"total_cont":0},{"name":"赤座灯里是勇者","count":140,"total_cont":0},{"name":"轻百合","count":124,"total_cont":0},{"name":"タカヒロ","count":82,"total_cont":0},{"name":"なもり","count":43,"total_cont":0},{"name":"萌","count":32,"total_cont":0},{"name":"さとう陽","count":27,"total_cont":0},{"name":"内田彩","count":19,"total_cont":0},{"name":"奇幻","count":15,"total_cont":0},{"name":"佐藤阳","count":14,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本","count":13,"total_cont":0},{"name":"校园","count":11,"total_cont":0},{"name":"沼仓爱美","count":11,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2018年","count":10,"total_cont":0},{"name":"月影特工","count":9,"total_cont":0},{"name":"间谍","count":8,"total_cont":0},{"name":"AkariPrincipal","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"レイ・デュース","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"特工","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"轻百","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本动画","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"季番","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"表番","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"洲崎绫","count":3,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":[{"key":"中文名"